     9	   contains a normative MUST. Per chapter 9 Â§3, the suite asserts
    10	   MUSTs only; SHOULDs and MAYs are interop guidance, not interop
    11	   contracts. The hierarchy walk lets a Â§3.2-level citation inherit
    12	   from a Â§3-level MUST.
    13	3. Every chapter-9 Â§5 scenario-index group has at least one citing test.
    14	
    15	Exit 0 on clean, 1 on unresolved citations, 2 on setup errors.
    16	"""
    17	
    18	from __future__ import annotations
    19	
    20	import ast
    21	import re
    22	import sys
    23	from pathlib import Path
